# English Only

## Invariant

All **new or edited** code, comments, docstrings, Cursor rules, and AI-drafted commit/PR text must be in **English**.

## STOP list

- Serbian/Cyrillic identifiers (`lista_slucajeva`, `predmet_id`) → use English names
- Serbian docstrings on new code → translate to English
- Mixed-language comments → English only

## Patterns

```python
# BAD
def lista_slucajeva():  # Vraća sve predmete
    ...

# GOOD
def list_cases():  # Returns cases owned by the current user
    ...
```

## Exceptions

- Future localized product copy under `docs/product/` (non-English user-facing text)
- Do not rename existing symbols solely for language — only when you touch that code

